author: Bill Bradley
title: 'The Walking Dead' Fans Think They Spotted An Unforgivable Error
text:
'The Walking Dead' Fans Think They Spotted An Unforgivable Error It's a bird. It's a ... hopefully, it's a bird. 
“ The Walking Dead ” has seemingly had a few subtle errors lately. 
There was Sasha’s trip and that house interior that appeared pretty fake, but the latest one is “plane” to see. AMC 
Yeah, supposedly there was airplane on “The Walking Dead.” 
While watching Sunday’s episode, many fans couldn’t help but notice the pretty obvious green screen behind Rick Grimes while he’s overlooking the dump. People could live with that, though. 
What they can’t live with is the thing flying in the background: Was that a plane behind Rick's head? Is it supposed to be there or is it a blooper? @WalkingDead_AMC pic.twitter.com/fqkuh4oJAJ — Molly Ehret (@MollyEhret) February 20, 2017 
During the scene, fans noticed an object traveling behind Rick’s head at a fairly high speed. Many believe it was a plane. @WalkingDead_AMC What was that flying behind Rick in the latest episode? Looked like a plane to me.
